# Cart Abandonment Workflow Automation

## Business Problem
E-commerce customers frequently abandon carts before completing a purchase, requiring timely follow-up to recover potential revenue.

## CRM Solution
A workflow rule was implemented in Zoho CRM to automatically trigger follow-up actions when a deal enters the **Cart Abandoned Follow-Up** stage.

## Trigger Conditions
- Module: Deals
- Trigger: On record create or edit
- Condition: Stage equals Cart Abandoned Follow-Up

## Automated Actions
- Automatically creates a follow-up task
- Task is assigned to the deal owner
- Due date is set to 2 days after the trigger

## Business Impact
- Eliminates manual follow-up tracking
- Ensures consistent outreach
- Improves conversion potential for abandoned carts
